name: Aneta ThinkOfAll
offering: Business Coaching, Business Consulting, Communication Training, Financial Coaches, Public Speaking
what_you_do: Aneta ThinkOfAll educates business leaders, women, and activists about the importance of making respectful choices and how to 'Think Of All' when making a choice so your choices help you and, when applicable, others.
who_you_serve: Business leaders, women, activists, and teens
seeking: Aneta is partnering with socially conscious activists and organizations that are working to promote respectfulness in their diverse communities and reduce social crimes such as human trafficking.
social_proof: Aneta has held many leadership positions in community service organizations and has served in an elected position as a councilwoman before moving to California.
business_focus: Educating business leaders, women, and activists on making respectful choices and decisions.
